metadata.name: It's Monday again 1
metadata.description:
It's Monday again
but I can swear it was just Friday a few hours ago.
Another day for some to show up with confidence and a disguise that says
 "oh how I love my job" 
And for others, a triple dose of dopamine.
Working keeps their soul alive.
Whatever it is. Does it really matter? 
We're all just striving hard to get the bag.
